  "response": "To find out when most of your Instagram followers are online, you can:\n\n1. Use Instagram Insights (for Business or Creator accounts)\n- Go to your profile\n- Tap the hamburger menu\n- Select \"Insights\"\n- Go to \"Audience\" tab\n- Scroll to see most active times/days\n\n2. Third-party analytics tools like:\n- Hootsuite\n- Sprout Social\n- Later\n- Buffer\n- Iconosquare\n\nThese tools provide detailed information about your followers' peak online times.\n\n3. General best practices suggest:\n- Weekdays: 11am-2pm and 7-9pm\n- Weekends: 11am-1pm and 7-9pm\n\nRemember that these times can vary based on your specific audience and their location/time zone.",
